{"word":"G793 - ἀστήρικτος - astḗriktos - as-tay'-rik-tos - Unstable","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀστήρικτος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">astḗriktos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">as-tay'-rik-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Unstable</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"உறுதியில்லாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"unstable"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivation of <a href=\"#/G4741 - στηρίζω - stērízō - stay-rid'-zo/4741\">G4741</a>; <i>unfixed</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>vacillating:</i> - unstable.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1991/1991\">G1991</a>, <a href=\"#/G4740/4740\">G4740</a>, <a href=\"#/G4741/4741\">G4741</a>, <a href=\"#/G793/793\">G793</a>"}]}